# ==========================================
# 4. Images
# ==========================================
# WARNING: This ignores ALL PNG files. If you use source PNGs 
# for your LaTeX figures, they will not be tracked or searchable.
*.png

# Alternative: If you only want to ignore images generated by 
# Python scripts or TikZ externalization, comment out "*.png" 
# above and use specific naming conventions like:
# *-generated.png
# tikz-cache/
# figure_output/

